wikipedia_page.main: Christopher Gane (born 5 June 1974) is an English professional golfer.Gane has mainly competed on the second tier Challenge Tour and has two wins on that tour, both in 2001. In 2009 he finished 13th in the Challenge Tour rankings to guarantee himself full European Tour status for 2010. He is one of the few left-handed players on tour.
